Synopsis: A library for generating 2D Charts and Plots
Description: A library for generating 2D Charts and Plots, based upon the cairo graphics library.
Category: Graphics
Cabal-Version: >= 1.6
Build-Type: Simple

Extra-Source-Files:
     tests/all_tests.hs,
     tests/Test1.hs,
     tests/Test2.hs,
     tests/Test3.hs,
     tests/Test4.hs,
     tests/Test5.hs,
